  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47668</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_063_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>やっぱり、朝は一杯の牛乳さんがいないと
始まんないと思うんだよね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ah! There's no better way to start a day than with a big cup of milk!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47740</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_063_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……オヤジくせー……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Ah this reeks of old hag...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47828</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_063_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そう？　どこが？
ここ？　ここかな？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Reaaally? Where's that old hag hiding? Here? Maybe here?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47912</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_063_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ちょっ……
ちか、近い近い……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>D-don't get close...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47984</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_063_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;、顔が赤いよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Dio&gt; your face is all red.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>48068</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_063_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>こ、これは……暑いんだっつーの！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I-It's just the weather is hot, that's all!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>48144</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_063_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;で楽しむの禁止です</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Seems like you're just having too much fun to me!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>48244</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_063_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そう？　んじゃあ、
&lt;Mel&gt;ちゃんで楽しんじゃお</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh, reaaally? Then I guess &lt;Mel&gt; wants all the fun for her~!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>48364</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_063_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、ちょっと……何するんですか、
&lt;Rody&gt;さん、あっ、そんなとこ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>W-what are you doing Miss &lt;Rody&gt;!? W-wah! Not there...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>48488</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_063_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ん～、&lt;Mel&gt;ちゃんも毎朝、牛乳さん飲んだ方が
ペッタンコ治るよ、たぶん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Mmm. &lt;Mel&gt; you also need to drink milk everyday if you don't want to be an ironing board!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>48576</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_002_063_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……ま、まだ成長期なんです～っ！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I-I still haven't hit my growth spurt--!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
